                            <comment id="12523045" author="mbenson" created="Mon, 27 Aug 2007 16:46:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The XPath spec is explicit on rounding, but less so on ceiling/floor.  However, the spec claims to use IEEE 754 which expresses ceiling/floor in terms of rounding, so I agree that abiding by the same rules in all cases is reasonable.  Thanks for the report, Sergey!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
